This paper deals with resource allocation in cellular networks, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses optimization problems and techniques for solving them, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of convex optimization, which is a common technique in multimedia processing (cs.MM) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
